132
00:07:16,140 --> 00:07:17,740
I lost the belief in that whole system.

133
00:07:18,020 --> 00:07:19,560
I lost the belief in academia.

134
00:07:19,560 --> 00:07:24,260
I lost the belief that I wanted to do that anymore.

135
00:07:24,260 --> 00:07:28,860
And I was totally obsessed with UFOs.

136
00:07:28,980 --> 00:07:33,740
I would remember for an entire year, I'd lie in bed, staring at the ceiling, thinking

137
00:07:33,740 --> 00:07:35,580
