138
00:07:35,760 --> 00:07:42,440
Like, if this is real, then was I totally wrong about everything I thought I knew about history?

139
00:07:43,060 --> 00:07:47,220
What is the truth then about the Truman administration that I was studying?

140
00:07:47,280 --> 00:07:48,400
Or Eisenhower or Kennedy?

141
00:07:48,400 --> 00:07:55,800
Like, there had to be this whole subterranean reality that I was oblivious to.

142
00:07:55,960 --> 00:08:00,320
And when you think you're a smart person and you think you're well-educated, that's the

143
00:08:00,320 --> 00:08:03,780
