144
00:08:03,920 --> 00:08:04,800
I had my ego.

145
00:08:05,200 --> 00:08:06,220
Like, absolutely.

146
00:08:06,500 --> 00:08:08,820
I want to be like, I'm a smart guy.

147
00:08:09,080 --> 00:08:10,100
