151
00:08:15,080 --> 00:08:19,360
No, it's not when your identity is so tied up in the system.

152
00:08:19,580 --> 00:08:25,260
The system's giving you positive feedback until that point to just accept, you know, that

153
00:08:25,260 --> 00:08:28,920
