154
00:08:29,000 --> 00:08:29,400
But you do.

155
00:08:29,500 --> 00:08:33,260
You read something like Timothy Good's, you know, Above Top Secret.

156
00:08:33,260 --> 00:08:38,840
And you're like, this is a whole ontology separate from, you know, the reality that I know.

157
